@user4 @user3 You can do it! And I'm happy to help you with my experiences.
Website: Check out @user5. It seems simple, looks good, and is open source. I will switch one of my websites to it before the next renewal.
Signal: Check out cal.com. It is an open-source calendar service with integrations that allow you to schedule video calls with Element Call, JITSI, etc. Signal is also supported, but I have not yet tested whether it works for messages or video.
I can recommend @user6. It offers end-to-end encryption, is decentralized, and open source.
